#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "आमुख"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is a rich educational software suite which contains a wide range "
"of activities."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; एकः समृद्धः शैक्षिकः सॉफ्टवेयर-समूहः अस्ति यस्मिन् विस्तृताः क्रियाकलापाः सन्ति "
"।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It offers various activities aimed at covering a variety of fields. The "
"topics include reading and typing, arithmetics, geography, sciences, and "
"other topics. It is meant to be used both at home and at school."
msgstr ""
"अत्र विविधक्षेत्राणां आच्छादनार्थं विविधानि कार्याणि प्रदत्तानि सन्ति । विषयेषु पठनं टङ्कनं "
"च, गणितं, भूगोलः, विज्ञानम्, अन्ये विषयाः सन्ति । गृहे विद्यालये च उपयोक्तुं अभिप्रेतम् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The purpose of &gcompris; is to provide playful activities but always "
"educational."
msgstr ""
"प्रयोजनं &gcompris; लीलायुक्तानि क्रियाकलापाः प्रदातुं किन्तु सर्वदा शिक्षाप्रदाः इति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is part of &kde; project and is placed under the <ulink url="
"\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">AGPLv3 license</ulink>. All "
"the code, except the engine for analog electricity activity is under <ulink "
"url=\"https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">GPLv3 license</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; &kde इत्यस्य भागः अस्ति; परियोजनायाः अन्तर्गतं <ulink url=\"https://www."
"gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.html\">AGPLv3 अनुज्ञापत्र</ulink> इत्यस्य अन्तर्गतं स्थापितं "
"भवति । एनालॉग् विद्युत्क्रियाकलापस्य इञ्जिनं विहाय सर्वः कोडः <ulink url=\"https://"
"www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl.html\">GPLv3 अनुज्ञापत्र</ulink> इत्यस्य अन्तर्गतः अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:82
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&gcompris; is available on the following operating systems: &GNU;/"
#| "&Linux;, &BSD;, MacOSX, &Windows;, Android. It requires a 3D card with "
#| "support of <emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> or higher. 32 bits color depth "
#| "mandatory."
msgid ""
"&gcompris; is available on the following operating systems: &GNU;/&Linux;, "
"&BSD;, &macOS;, &Windows;, Android. It requires a 3D card with support of "
"<emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> or higher. 32 bits color depth is mandatory."
msgstr ""
"&gcompris; निम्नलिखितप्रचालनतन्त्रेषु उपलभ्यते: &GNU;/&Linux;, &BSD;, MacOSX, "
"&Windows;, Android. अस्य कृते <emphasis>OpenGL 2.1</emphasis> अथवा उच्चतरस्य "
"समर्थनयुक्तं 3D कार्ड् आवश्यकम् । ३२ बिट् वर्णगहनता अनिवार्यम्।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "स्थापना"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The software is delivered under several forms. Follow the process according "
"to your case."
msgstr "सॉफ्टवेयरं अनेकरूपेण वितरितं भवति । स्वप्रकरणानुसारं प्रक्रियां अनुसरणं कुर्वन्तु।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:90
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&GNU;/&Linux;: use the packages delivered by your &GNU;/&Linux; "
#| "distribution. If &gcompris; is not packaged in your &Linux; distribution, "
#| "please contact them to ask for the inclusion of &gcompris; in your "
#| "&Linux; distribution."
msgid ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: use the packages delivered by your &GNU;/&Linux; "
"distribution. If &gcompris; is not packaged in your &Linux; distribution, "
"please contact them to ask for the inclusion of &gcompris;."
msgstr ""
"&GNU;/&Linux;: भवतः &GNU;/&Linux; आवंटन। यदि &gcompris; भवतः &Linux; वितरणं "
"कृत्वा, कृपया तेषां सम्पर्कं कृत्वा &gcompris; भवतः &Linux; आवंटन।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&Windows;: delivered under a classic installer for &Windows; or via the "
"Microsoft Store."
msgstr ""
"&Windows;: &Windows;: कृते एकस्य क्लासिकस्य संस्थापकस्य अन्तर्गतं वितरितम्; अथवा "
"Microsoft Store मार्गेण।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:92
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "MacOSX: delivered under a classic installer."
msgid "&macOS;: delivered under a classic installer."
msgstr "MacOSX: एकस्य क्लासिकस्य संस्थापकस्य अन्तर्गतं वितरितम्।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Android: distributed by the F-Droid store or Google Play Store. Apk file "
#| "is also available."
msgid ""
"Android: distributed by the F-Droid store or Google Play Store. APK file is "
"also available."
msgstr ""
"एण्ड्रॉयड् : F-Droid भण्डारेण अथवा Google Play Store द्वारा वितरितम् । Apk सञ्चिका "
"अपि उपलभ्यते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "The User Interface"
msgstr "उपयोक्तृ-अन्तरफलकम्"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The interface is designed for easy use by small children. &gcompris; is "
"controlled with a mouse. Keyboard navigation is also available on most of "
"the activities."
msgstr ""
"लघुबालानां सुलभप्रयोगाय अन्तरफलकं विनिर्मितम् अस्ति । &gcompris; मूषकेन नियन्त्र्यते । "
"अधिकांशेषु कार्येषु कीबोर्ड-सञ्चारः अपि उपलभ्यते ।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main window"
msgstr "मुख्यविण्डो"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When you start the program, &gcompris; shows a graphic interface which "
#| "presents the list of activities with a control bar at the bottom."
msgid ""
"When you start the program, &gcompris; shows a graphical interface which "
"presents the list of activities with a control bar at the bottom."
msgstr ""
"यदा भवन्तः कार्यक्रमं आरभन्ते तदा &gcompris; एकं चित्रात्मकं अन्तरफलकं दर्शयति यत् अधः "
"नियन्त्रणपट्टिकायाः सह क्रियाकलापानाम् सूचीं प्रस्तुतं करोति ।"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:105
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Here's a screenshot of &gcompris; Main Window"
msgid "Here’s a screenshot of &gcompris; main window"
msgstr "अत्र &gcompris; मुख्य खिडकी"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gcompris; Main Window"
msgstr "&gcompris; मुख्य खिडकी"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:116
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Each icon represents an activity. Around each one, you can find small "
#| "icons which give additional information about the activity. A simple "
#| "click on the icon will lead you to an activity or a menu of activities. "
#| "There are 8 sections (categories) of activities, which are placed on the "
#| "top or on the left (only if your orientation is portrait). For example, "
#| "there is section \"Board games\", which includes board games, like chess, "
#| "tic tac toe or align four."
msgid ""
"Each icon represents an activity. Around each one, you can find small icons "
"which give additional information about the activity. A simple click on the "
"icon will lead you to an activity or a menu of activities. There are 8 "
"sections (categories) of activities, which are placed on the top or on the "
"left (only if your orientation is portrait). For example, there is section "
"“Board Games”, which includes board games, like Chess, Tic-Tac-Toe or Align "
"Four."
msgstr ""
"प्रत्येकं चिह्नं एकं क्रियाकलापं प्रतिनिधियति । प्रत्येकस्य परितः भवन्तः लघुचिह्नानि द्रष्टुं "
"शक्नुवन्ति ये क्रियाकलापस्य विषये अतिरिक्तसूचनाः ददति । चिह्नस्य उपरि सरलं क्लिक् कृत्वा "
"भवन्तः कस्यापि क्रियाकलापस्य अथवा क्रियाकलापस्य मेन्यू इत्यस्य कृते गच्छन्ति । "
"क्रियाकलापानाम् ८ विभागाः (वर्गाः) सन्ति, ये उपरि वामे वा स्थापिताः सन्ति (यदि भवतः "
"अभिमुखीकरणं चित्रम् अस्ति एव) । यथा, \"Board games\" इति विभागः अस्ति, यस्मिन् "
"बोर्डक्रीडाः सन्ति, यथा शतरंजः, tic tac toe अथवा align four इत्यादयः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some categories have subcategories to better filter the activities. For math "
"activities, we have three subcategories: numeration, arithmetic and measures."
msgstr ""
"केषुचित् वर्गेषु क्रियाकलापानाम् उत्तमरीत्या छाननाय उपवर्गाः सन्ति । गणितक्रियाणां कृते "
"अस्माकं त्रयः उपवर्गाः सन्ति- संख्या, गणितं, मापः च ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "The stars indicate the age group for which each game is designed:"
msgstr "ताराणि तस्य आयुवर्गस्य सूचकाः सन्ति यस्य कृते प्रत्येकं क्रीडा परिकल्पिता अस्ति :"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "1, 2 or 3 yellow stars - for 2 to 6 years old."
msgid "1, 2 or 3 yellow stars — for 2 to 6 years old."
msgstr "१, २ वा ३ पीततारकाणि - २ तः ६ वर्षाणि यावत् ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "1, 2 or 3 red stars - greater than 6 years old."
msgid "1, 2 or 3 red stars — greater than 6 years old."
msgstr "१, २ वा ३ रक्ततारकाः - ६ वर्षाणाम् अधिकाः ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the screen there is a control bar for &gcompris;. The "
"possible icons are (the icons are only displayed if they are available in "
"the activity):"
msgstr ""
"स्क्रीनस्य अधः &gcompris; इत्यस्य नियन्त्रणपट्टिका अस्ति । सम्भाव्यचिह्नानि सन्ति "
"(चिह्नानि केवलं तदा एव प्रदर्श्यन्ते यदा ते क्रियाकलापस्य मध्ये उपलब्धाः सन्ति):"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Home - Leaves the current activity, returns to the previous menu."
msgid "Home — Leaves the current activity, returns to the previous menu."
msgstr "गृहम् - वर्तमानक्रियाकलापं त्यजति, पूर्वमेनू प्रति प्रत्यागच्छति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "\"OK\" - Validate, confirm your answer. Some activities do not detect "
#| "automatically whether or not the child has completed the task. In this "
#| "case, you have to click on this icon. You can also use the &Enter; key on "
#| "your keyboard."
msgid ""
"“OK” — Validate, confirm your answer. Some activities do not detect "
"automatically whether or not the child has completed the task. In this case, "
"you have to click on this icon. You can also use the &Enter; key on your "
"keyboard."
msgstr ""
"\"ठीकम्\" - प्रमाणयन्तु, भवतः उत्तरस्य पुष्टिं कुर्वन्तु। केचन क्रियाकलापाः स्वयमेव न ज्ञायन्ते "
"यत् बालेन कार्यं सम्पन्नं वा न वा । अस्मिन् सति भवद्भिः एतत् चिह्नं क्लिक् कर्तव्यम् । भवन्तः "
"&Enter; कीलं भवतः कीबोर्ड् मध्ये।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Light - Display a hint for the activity. We can help the children on some "
#| "activities to guide them to find the answers."
msgid ""
"Light — Display a hint for the activity. We can help the children on some "
"activities to guide them to find the answers."
msgstr ""
"प्रकाश - क्रियाकलापस्य कृते एकं संकेतं प्रदर्शयन्तु। वयं बालकानां उत्तराणि अन्वेष्टुं मार्गदर्शनं "
"कर्तुं केषुचित् कार्येषु साहाय्यं कर्तुं शक्नुमः।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:138
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Arrows - The present level is displayed. Click on one of the arrows to "
#| "select another level. Generally, the activities offer several levels "
#| "whose numbers depend on the activity. In &gcompris;, it is possible to go "
#| "to the next level without having completed the current level."
msgid ""
"Arrows — The present level is displayed. Click on one of the arrows to "
"select another level. Generally, the activities offer several levels whose "
"numbers depend on the activity. In &gcompris;, it is possible to go to the "
"next level without having completed the current level."
msgstr ""
"बाणाः - वर्तमानस्तरः प्रदर्शितः भवति । अन्यं स्तरं चिन्वितुं बाणेषु एकस्मिन् नुदन्तु । "
"सामान्यतया क्रियाकलापाः अनेकस्तराः प्रददति येषां संख्या क्रियाकलापस्य आधारेण भवति । "
"&gcompris;मध्ये वर्तमानस्तरं न सम्पन्नं कृत्वा अग्रिमस्तरं गन्तुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Lips - Ask &gcompris; to repeat the question."
msgid "Lips — Ask &gcompris; to repeat the question."
msgstr "अधरम् - पृच्छतु &gcompris; प्रश्नं पुनः पुनः कर्तुं ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:144
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Question mark - Display the help dialog box. Sometimes, an activity can "
#| "be too complex to be described easily in the description area. In this "
#| "case, this function gives access to additional information."
msgid ""
"Question mark — Display the help dialog box. Sometimes, an activity can be "
"too complex to be described easily in the description area. In this case, "
"this function gives access to additional information."
msgstr ""
"प्रश्नचिह्नम् - सहायतासंवादपेटिकां प्रदर्शयन्तु। कदाचित्, कश्चन क्रियाकलापः अत्यन्तं जटिलः "
"भवितुम् अर्हति यत् वर्णनक्षेत्रे सुलभतया वर्णयितुं न शक्यते । अस्मिन् सन्दर्भे एतत् कार्यं "
"अतिरिक्तसूचनानाम् अभिगमनं ददाति ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:146
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Tool box - Configuration menu. The configuration is saved in the user "
#| "repository (folder) under the name <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris-qt."
#| "conf</filename>. This is a text file which can be edited manually."
msgid ""
"Tool box — Configuration menu. The configuration is saved in the user "
"repository (folder) under the name <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris-qt."
"conf</filename>. This is a text file which can be edited manually."
msgstr ""
"साधनपेटी - विन्यासमेनू। विन्यासः <filename>.config/gcompris/gcompris-qt.conf</"
"filename> इति नाम्ना उपयोक्तृभण्डारे (पुटे) रक्षितः भवति । इयं पाठसञ्चिका अस्ति या "
"हस्तचलितरूपेण सम्पादयितुं शक्यते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:148
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "List item - Display the activity settings menu. There are two possible "
#| "tabs here. First one, \"Dataset\", allows to choose the levels of the "
#| "activities depending on several objectives and the second one, \"Options"
#| "\", allows to update the configuration of the activity if available."
